nodes.text: Unidentified Acclamator-class transgalactic military assault ship (Saleucami)

This Acclamator-class transgalactic military assault ship was used by the Galactic Republic during the Clone Wars. During the Battle of Saleucami, it was used to transport Jedi General Obi-Wan Kenobi, Clone Commander Cody and the 501st Legion to the surface of Saleucami.
